{
  "video_id": "j4RPuNE2f9Q",
  "title": "Joy and Spiritual Survival",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 550.0,
      "end_time": 2660.0,
      "text": "Thank you, President Monson."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2660.0,
      "end_time": 6240.0,
      "text": "We love and sustain you."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6240.0,
      "end_time": 8370.0,
      "text": "My dear brothers and sisters, today I"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8370.0,
      "end_time": 10469.0,
      "text": "would like to discuss a principle that is"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10470.0,
      "end_time": 13940.0,
      "text": "key to our spiritual survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13940.0,
      "end_time": 16970.0,
      "text": "It is a principle that will only become"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16970.0,
      "end_time": 20650.0,
      "text": "more important as the tragedies and travesties around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20650.0,
      "end_time": 22939.0,
      "text": "increase."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22940.0,
      "end_time": 26230.0,
      "text": "These are the latter days, so none of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26230.0,
      "end_time": 30230.0,
      "text": "should be surprised when we see prophecy fulfilled."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30230.0,
      "end_time": 35200.0,
      "text": "A host of prophets, including Isaiah, Paul, Nephi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35200.0,
      "end_time": 39810.0,
      "text": "and Mormon, foresaw that perilous times would come,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39810.0,
      "end_time": 44310.0,
      "text": "that in our day the whole world would be in commotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44310.0,
      "end_time": 48340.0,
      "text": "that men would \"be lovers of their own selves, . . ."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48340.0,
      "end_time": 52500.0,
      "text": "without natural affection, . . . lovers of pleasures more than"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52500.0,
      "end_time": 57540.0,
      "text": "lovers of God,\" and that many would become servants of Satan"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57540.0,
      "end_time": 60370.0,
      "text": "who uphold the adversary&#39;s work."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60370.0,
      "end_time": 63699.0,
      "text": "Indeed, you and I \"wrestle . . . against the rulers"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63700.0,
      "end_time": 66570.0,
      "text": "of the darkness of this world, [and] against spiritual"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66570.0,
      "end_time": 69649.0,
      "text": "wickedness in high places.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69650.0,
      "end_time": 73110.0,
      "text": "As conflicts between nations escalate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73110.0,
      "end_time": 77860.0,
      "text": "as cowardly terrorists prey on the innocent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77860.0,
      "end_time": 81730.0,
      "text": "and as corruption in everything from business to government"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81730.0,
      "end_time": 86380.0,
      "text": "becomes increasingly commonplace, what can help us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86380.0,
      "end_time": 90890.0,
      "text": "What can help each of us with our personal struggles"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90890.0,
      "end_time": 95850.0,
      "text": "and with the rigorous challenge of living in these latter days?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95850.0,
      "end_time": 97979.0,
      "text": "The prophet Lehi taught a principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97980.0,
      "end_time": 99910.0,
      "text": "for spiritual survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99910.0,
      "end_time": 102380.0,
      "text": "First, consider his circumstances:"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102380.0,
      "end_time": 105649.0,
      "text": "He had been persecuted for preaching truth in Jerusalem"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105650.0,
      "end_time": 108700.0,
      "text": "and had been commanded by the Lord to leave his possessions"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108700.0,
      "end_time": 111650.0,
      "text": "and flee with his family into the wilderness."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111650.0,
      "end_time": 114540.0,
      "text": "He had lived in a tent and survived"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114540.0,
      "end_time": 117310.0,
      "text": "on what food could be found on the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117310.0,
      "end_time": 120150.0,
      "text": "to an unknown destination, and he"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120150.0,
      "end_time": 122860.0,
      "text": "had watched two of his sons, Laman and Lemuel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122860.0,
      "end_time": 124810.0,
      "text": "rebel against the teachings of the Lord"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124810.0,
      "end_time": 128190.0,
      "text": "and attack their brothers Nephi and Sam."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128190.0,
      "end_time": 135859.0,
      "text": "Clearly, Lehi knew opposition, anxiety, heartache, pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135860.0,
      "end_time": 138550.0,
      "text": "disappointment, and sorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138550.0,
      "end_time": 142560.0,
      "text": "Yet he declared boldly and without reservation a principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142560.0,
      "end_time": 150690.0,
      "text": "as revealed by the Lord: \"Men are, that they might have joy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150690.0,
      "end_time": 152740.0,
      "text": "Imagine!"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152740.0,
      "end_time": 155430.0,
      "text": "Of all the words he could have used"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 155430.0,
      "end_time": 157450.0,
      "text": "to describe the nature and purpose of our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157450.0,
      "end_time": 160535.0,
      "text": "here in mortality, he chose the word joy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 163360.0,
      "end_time": 167320.0,
      "text": "Life is filled with detours and dead ends, trials"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167320.0,
      "end_time": 169700.0,
      "text": "and challenges of every kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 169700.0,
      "end_time": 174109.0,
      "text": "Each of us has likely had times when distress, anguish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174110.0,
      "end_time": 176680.0,
      "text": "and despair almost consumed us."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176680.0,
      "end_time": 181230.0,
      "text": "Yet we are here to have joy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 181230.0,
      "end_time": 182549.0,
      "text": "Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182550.0,
      "end_time": 186920.0,
      "text": "The answer is a resounding yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 186920.0,
      "end_time": 189959.0,
      "text": "But how is that possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189960.0,
      "end_time": 195100.0,
      "text": "And what must we do to claim the joy that Heavenly Father has"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 195100.0,
      "end_time": 198650.0,
      "text": "in store for us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 198650.0,
      "end_time": 202320.0,
      "text": "Eliza R. Snow, second General President"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 202320.0,
      "end_time": 205750.0,
      "text": "of the Relief Society, offered a riveting answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 205750.0,
      "end_time": 210530.0,
      "text": "Because of Missouri&#39;s infamous extermination order"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 210530.0,
      "end_time": 215800.0,
      "text": "issued at the onset of the grueling winter of 1838,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 215800.0,
      "end_time": 219750.0,
      "text": "she and other Saints were forced to flee the state"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 219750.0,
      "end_time": 223430.0,
      "text": "that very winter."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 223430.0,
      "end_time": 225790.0,
      "text": "One evening, Eliza&#39;s family spent the night"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 225790.0,
      "end_time": 229780.0,
      "text": "in a small log cabin used by refugee Saints."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 229780.0,
      "end_time": 232370.0,
      "text": "Much of the chinking between the logs"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 232370.0,
      "end_time": 235800.0,
      "text": "had been extracted and burned for firewood"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 235800.0,
      "end_time": 238100.0,
      "text": "by those who preceded them, so there"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 238100.0,
      "end_time": 242440.0,
      "text": "were holes between the logs large enough for a cat"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 242440.0,
      "end_time": 243470.0,
      "text": "to crawl through."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 243470.0,
      "end_time": 251490.0,
      "text": "It was bitter cold, and their food was frozen solid."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251490.0,
      "end_time": 253610.0,
      "text": "That night some 80 people huddled"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 253610.0,
      "end_time": 257550.0,
      "text": "inside that small cabin, only 20 feet square."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257550.0,
      "end_time": 262600.0,
      "text": "Most sat or stood all night trying to keep warm."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 262600.0,
      "end_time": 265250.0,
      "text": "Outside, a group of men spent the night"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 265250.0,
      "end_time": 269370.0,
      "text": "gathered around a roaring fire, with some singing songs"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 269370.0,
      "end_time": 273700.0,
      "text": "and others roasting frozen potatoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273700.0,
      "end_time": 280500.0,
      "text": "Eliza recorded: \"Not a complaint was heard--all were cheerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 280500.0,
      "end_time": 284490.0,
      "text": "and judging from appearances, strangers would have taken us"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 284490.0,
      "end_time": 288870.0,
      "text": "to be pleasure excursionists rather than a band"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 288870.0,
      "end_time": 293900.0,
      "text": "of gubernatorial exiles.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 293900.0,
      "end_time": 297370.0,
      "text": "Eliza&#39;s report of that exhausting, bone-chilling"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 297370.0,
      "end_time": 300110.0,
      "text": "evening was strikingly optimistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 300110.0,
      "end_time": 306200.0,
      "text": "She declared: \"That was a very merry night."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 306200.0,
      "end_time": 312109.0,
      "text": "None but saints can be happy under every circumstance.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 312110.0,
      "end_time": 313270.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 313270.0,
      "end_time": 317229.0,
      "text": "Saints can be happy under every circumstance."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 317230.0,
      "end_time": 321820.0,
      "text": "We can feel joy even while having a bad day, a bad week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 321820.0,
      "end_time": 324930.0,
      "text": "or even a bad year!"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 324930.0,
      "end_time": 327230.0,
      "text": "My dear brothers and sisters, the joy we feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 327230.0,
      "end_time": 330770.0,
      "text": "has little to do with the circumstances of our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 330770.0,
      "end_time": 337640.0,
      "text": "and everything to do with the focus of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 337640.0,
      "end_time": 341770.0,
      "text": "When the focus of our lives is on God&#39;s plan of salvation that"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 341770.0,
      "end_time": 348500.0,
      "text": "President Monson just taught us and Jesus&#39;s gospel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 348500.0,
      "end_time": 351910.0,
      "text": "we can feel joy regardless of what is happening--or not"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 351910.0,
      "end_time": 354360.0,
      "text": "happening--in our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 354360.0,
      "end_time": 358660.0,
      "text": "Joy comes from and because of Him."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 358660.0,
      "end_time": 362460.0,
      "text": "He is the source of all joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 362460.0,
      "end_time": 367690.0,
      "text": "We feel it at Christmastime when we sing, \"Joy to the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 367690.0,
      "end_time": 370150.0,
      "text": "the Lord is come.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 370150.0,
      "end_time": 373419.0,
      "text": "And we can feel it all year round."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 373420.0,
      "end_time": 379910.0,
      "text": "For Latter-day Saints, Jesus Christ is joy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 379910.0,
      "end_time": 381990.0,
      "text": "That is why our missionaries leave their homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 381990.0,
      "end_time": 384230.0,
      "text": "to preach His gospel."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 384230.0,
      "end_time": 388900.0,
      "text": "Their goal is not to increase the number of Church members."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 388900.0,
      "end_time": 392780.0,
      "text": "Rather, our missionaries teach and baptize to bring joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 392780.0,
      "end_time": 394349.0,
      "text": "to the people of the world!"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 396930.0,
      "end_time": 399140.0,
      "text": "Just as the Savior offers peace that"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 399140.0,
      "end_time": 401539.0,
      "text": "\"passeth all understanding,\" He also offers"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 401540.0,
      "end_time": 405160.0,
      "text": "an intensity, depth, and breadth of joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 405160.0,
      "end_time": 409440.0,
      "text": "that defy human logic or mortal comprehension."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 409440.0,
      "end_time": 414490.0,
      "text": "For example, it doesn&#39;t seem possible to feel joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 414490.0,
      "end_time": 418170.0,
      "text": "when your child suffers with an incurable illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 418170.0,
      "end_time": 424170.0,
      "text": "or when you lose your job or when your spouse betrays you."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 424170.0,
      "end_time": 428300.0,
      "text": "Yet that is precisely the joy the Savior offers."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 428300.0,
      "end_time": 432840.0,
      "text": "His joy is constant, assuring us that our \"afflictions"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 432840.0,
      "end_time": 439739.0,
      "text": "shall be but a small moment\" and be consecrated to our gain."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 439740.0,
      "end_time": 442680.0,
      "text": "How, then, can we claim that joy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 442680.0,
      "end_time": 446970.0,
      "text": "We can start by \"looking unto Jesus the author"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 446970.0,
      "end_time": 451800.0,
      "text": "and finisher of our faith\" \"in every thought.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 451800.0,
      "end_time": 454850.0,
      "text": "We can give thanks for Him in our prayers"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 454850.0,
      "end_time": 457810.0,
      "text": "and by keeping covenants we&#39;ve made with Him and our Heavenly"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 457810.0,
      "end_time": 460540.0,
      "text": "Father."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 460540.0,
      "end_time": 464200.0,
      "text": "As our Savior becomes more and more real to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 464200.0,
      "end_time": 468170.0,
      "text": "and as we plead for His joy to be given to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 468170.0,
      "end_time": 471430.0,
      "text": "our joy will increase."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 471430.0,
      "end_time": 475250.0,
      "text": "Joy is powerful, and focusing on joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 475250.0,
      "end_time": 478970.0,
      "text": "brings God&#39;s power into our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 478970.0,
      "end_time": 483750.0,
      "text": "As in all things, Jesus Christ is our ultimate exemplar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 483750.0,
      "end_time": 491600.0,
      "text": "\"who for the joy that was set before him endured the cross.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 491600.0,
      "end_time": 493520.0,
      "text": "Think of that!"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 493520.0,
      "end_time": 498370.0,
      "text": "In order for Him to endure the most excruciating experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 498370.0,
      "end_time": 505540.0,
      "text": "ever endured on earth, our Savior focused on joy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 505540.0,
      "end_time": 509290.0,
      "text": "And what was the joy that was set before Him?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 509290.0,
      "end_time": 513120.0,
      "text": "Surely it included the joy of cleansing, healing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 513120.0,
      "end_time": 519750.0,
      "text": "and strengthening us; the joy of paying for the sins of all who"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 519750.0,
      "end_time": 524390.0,
      "text": "would repent; the joy of making it possible for you and me"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 524390.0,
      "end_time": 528240.0,
      "text": "to return home--clean and worthy--to live with"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 528240.0,
      "end_time": 531720.0,
      "text": "our Heavenly Parents and families."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 531720.0,
      "end_time": 536760.0,
      "text": "If we focus on the joy that will come to us or to those we love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 536760.0,
      "end_time": 539780.0,
      "text": "what can we endure that presently"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 539780.0,
      "end_time": 543610.0,
      "text": "seems overwhelming, painful, scary, unfair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 543610.0,
      "end_time": 547280.0,
      "text": "or simply impossible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 547280.0,
      "end_time": 551400.0,
      "text": "One father in a spiritually precarious situation focused"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 551400.0,
      "end_time": 554319.0,
      "text": "on the joy of finally being clean and right with"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 554320.0,
      "end_time": 561130.0,
      "text": "the Lord--the joy of being freed from guilt and shame--and"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 561130.0,
      "end_time": 563630.0,
      "text": "the joy of having peace of mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 563630.0,
      "end_time": 566480.0,
      "text": "That focus gave him the courage to confess"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 566480.0,
      "end_time": 569300.0,
      "text": "to his wife and bishop about his problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 569300.0,
      "end_time": 573290.0,
      "text": "with pornography and his subsequent infidelity."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 573290.0,
      "end_time": 577530.0,
      "text": "He is now doing everything his bishop counsels him to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 577530.0,
      "end_time": 581160.0,
      "text": "striving with all his heart to regain"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 581160.0,
      "end_time": 586000.0,
      "text": "the trust of his dear wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 586000.0,
      "end_time": 590380.0,
      "text": "A young woman focused on the joy of staying sexually pure"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 590380.0,
      "end_time": 593150.0,
      "text": "to help her endure the mocking of friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 593150.0,
      "end_time": 596100.0,
      "text": "as she walked away from a popular and provocative"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 596100.0,
      "end_time": 600450.0,
      "text": "but spiritually dangerous situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 600450.0,
      "end_time": 603380.0,
      "text": "A man who frequently demeaned his wife"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 603380.0,
      "end_time": 607800.0,
      "text": "and indulged in angry outbursts at his children"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 607800.0,
      "end_time": 610690.0,
      "text": "focused on the joy of being worthy to have the Holy Ghost"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 610690.0,
      "end_time": 612970.0,
      "text": "as his constant companion."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 612970.0,
      "end_time": 615760.0,
      "text": "That focus motivated him to put off"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 615760.0,
      "end_time": 619710.0,
      "text": "the natural man, to which he had too often succumbed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 619710.0,
      "end_time": 624170.0,
      "text": "and make needed changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 624170.0,
      "end_time": 627120.0,
      "text": "A dear colleague recently told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 627120.0,
      "end_time": 631800.0,
      "text": "of his past two decades of heavy trials."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 631800.0,
      "end_time": 638410.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I have learned to suffer--with joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 638410.0,
      "end_time": 646530.0,
      "text": "My suffering was swallowed up in the joy of Christ.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 646530.0,
      "end_time": 648650.0,
      "text": "What will you and I be able to endure"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 648650.0,
      "end_time": 652130.0,
      "text": "as we focus on the joy that is \"set before\" us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 652130.0,
      "end_time": 655250.0,
      "text": "What repenting will then be possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 655250.0,
      "end_time": 658500.0,
      "text": "What weakness will become a strength?"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 658500.0,
      "end_time": 662100.0,
      "text": "What chastening will become a blessing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 662100.0,
      "end_time": 665890.0,
      "text": "What disappointments, even tragedies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 665890.0,
      "end_time": 668340.0,
      "text": "will turn to our good?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 668340.0,
      "end_time": 670540.0,
      "text": "And what challenging service to the Lord"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 670540.0,
      "end_time": 673520.0,
      "text": "will we be able to give?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 673520.0,
      "end_time": 676449.0,
      "text": "As we diligently focus on the Savior"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 676450.0,
      "end_time": 680480.0,
      "text": "and then follow His pattern of focusing on joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 680480.0,
      "end_time": 683815.0,
      "text": "we need to avoid those things that can interrupt our joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 686600.0,
      "end_time": 689630.0,
      "text": "Remember Korihor, the anti-Christ?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 689630.0,
      "end_time": 692400.0,
      "text": "Spewing falsehoods about the Savior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 692400.0,
      "end_time": 694840.0,
      "text": "Korihor went from place to place until he"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 694840.0,
      "end_time": 697750.0,
      "text": "was brought before a high priest who asked him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 697750.0,
      "end_time": 701940.0,
      "text": "\"Why do ye go about perverting the ways of the Lord?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 701940.0,
      "end_time": 705350.0,
      "text": "Why do ye teach this people that there shall be no Christ,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 705350.0,
      "end_time": 708880.0,
      "text": "to interrupt their rejoicings?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 708880.0,
      "end_time": 712970.0,
      "text": "Anything that opposes Christ or His doctrine"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 712970.0,
      "end_time": 716000.0,
      "text": "will interrupt our joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 716000.0,
      "end_time": 721540.0,
      "text": "That includes the philosophies of men, so abundant online"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 721540.0,
      "end_time": 726360.0,
      "text": "and in the blogosphere, which do exactly what Korihor did."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 728950.0,
      "end_time": 731650.0,
      "text": "If we look to the world and follow its formulas"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 731650.0,
      "end_time": 735600.0,
      "text": "for happiness, we will never know joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 735600.0,
      "end_time": 738800.0,
      "text": "The unrighteous may experience any number"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 738800.0,
      "end_time": 745130.0,
      "text": "of emotions and sensations, but they will never experience joy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 745130.0,
      "end_time": 747330.0,
      "text": "Joy is a gift for the faithful."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 747330.0,
      "end_time": 750740.0,
      "text": "It is the gift that comes from intentionally"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 750740.0,
      "end_time": 756750.0,
      "text": "trying to live a righteous life, as taught by Jesus Christ."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 756750.0,
      "end_time": 759270.0,
      "text": "He taught us how to have joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 759270.0,
      "end_time": 762380.0,
      "text": "When we choose Heavenly Father to be our God"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 762380.0,
      "end_time": 764540.0,
      "text": "and when we can feel the Savior&#39;s Atonement"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 764540.0,
      "end_time": 768640.0,
      "text": "working in our lives, we will be filled with joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 768640.0,
      "end_time": 772280.0,
      "text": "Every time we nurture our spouse and guide"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 772280.0,
      "end_time": 776230.0,
      "text": "our children, every time we forgive someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 776230.0,
      "end_time": 782150.0,
      "text": "or ask for their forgiveness, we can feel joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 782150.0,
      "end_time": 785890.0,
      "text": "Every day that you and I choose to live celestial laws,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 785890.0,
      "end_time": 788189.0,
      "text": "every day that we keep our covenants"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 788190.0,
      "end_time": 794200.0,
      "text": "and help others to do the same, joy will be ours."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 794200.0,
      "end_time": 798000.0,
      "text": "Heed these words of the Psalmist:"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 798000.0,
      "end_time": 802990.0,
      "text": "\"I have set the Lord always before me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 802990.0,
      "end_time": 808250.0,
      "text": "because he is at my right hand, I shall not be moved."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 808250.0,
      "end_time": 809310.0,
      "text": ". . ."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 809310.0,
      "end_time": 815589.0,
      "text": "In [His] presence is fulness of joy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 815590.0,
      "end_time": 821630.0,
      "text": "As this principle is embedded in our hearts, each and every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 821630.0,
      "end_time": 825840.0,
      "text": "can be a day of joy and gladness."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 825840.0,
      "end_time": 831780.0,
      "text": "I so testify in the sacred name of Jesus Christ, amen."
    }
  ]
}